<li><a href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Extensible_Application_Markup_Language" title="Extensible Application Markup Language">XAML</a> User interface language using vector graphics for images.</li></ul><h3 class="in-block"><span class="mw-headline" id="Stereo_formats">Stereo formats</span><span class="mw-editsection"><a href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Image_file_formats&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Edit section: Stereo formats" data-section="27" class="mw-ui-icon mw-ui-icon-element mw-ui-icon-minerva-edit-enabled edit-page">Edit</a></span></h3>
